summary: Successfully re-implemented tabindex functionality for the search interface. Added proper tabindex values to all interactive elements: search input (1), search button (2), category buttons (3-7), other/custom input (8), and quick completion pills (9-12). Also updated the AutoCompleteSearch component to accept tabIndex prop and fixed duplicate tabindex attributes.
current_status: Search interface now has proper keyboard navigation with logical tab order starting from the search input, followed by the search button, then category selection buttons, and finally quick completion suggestions.
